<h2 id="h-what-is-zoom" class="wp-block-heading">What is Zoom?</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>What is Zoom?<br /><br />Zoom is a powerful video conferencing platform that allows users to connect with others through high-quality audio and video calls. It offers a seamless way to conduct meetings, webinars, virtual events, and even social gatherings – all from the comfort of your own device. With its user-friendly interface and robust features, Zoom has gained immense popularity worldwide.<br /><br />One of the standout features of Zoom is its ability to host large group meetings with up to hundreds or even thousands of participants. This makes it an ideal choice for businesses, educational institutions, and organizations looking for a reliable solution for remote collaboration.<br /><br />Apart from its impressive scalability, Zoom also offers several interactive tools such as screen sharing, chat functionalities, breakout rooms, virtual backgrounds, and more. These features enhance user engagement and make communication more dynamic.<br /><br />Moreover, Zoom provides excellent audio and video quality even in low-bandwidth situations. This ensures that you can have crystal-clear conversations regardless of your internet connection strength.<br /><br />In essence, Zoom brings people together in real-time irrespective of their physical location. So whether you're conducting business meetings or catching up with friends across continents, this innovative app has got you covered!</p>
